summary: An ordinance relating to zoning, establishing Use, Height and Area Districts for a portion of the northwest quarter of the northeast quarter of the northeast quarter of Section 1, Township 23 North, Range 3 East, W. M., annexed to the City of Seattle under Ordinance No. 74757 and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto three new sections numbered 2-176, 10-8, and 17-126, respectively.
